00:34:31.630 --> 00:34:33.210
na sa ibinigay kay Cangcang,

00:34:33.480 --> 00:34:34.860
hindi lamang nakamamatay na lason

00:34:36.110 --> 00:34:37.130
kundi pati na rin ang Lovesickness Powder.

00:35:00.320 --> 00:35:01.820
Nakakita kami ng mahalagang lead:

00:35:02.110 --> 00:35:03.610
ang lunas sa malamig na sakit ng Kanyang Kamahalan,

00:35:03.630 --> 00:35:04.380
ang bihirang Frost Reed,

00:35:04.540 --> 00:35:05.690
ay sa wakas ay natagpuan.

00:35:08.590 --> 00:35:10.470
Kung ilalagay natin ang Lovesickness Powder at ang lason

00:35:11.880 --> 00:35:14.210
tanging sa pinakatuktok na layer ng pulot,

00:35:14.800 --> 00:35:17.460
masisiguro mo bang malinis ang pulot sa ilalim?

00:35:17.880 --> 00:35:18.780
Kaya ko, panginoon.

00:35:19.280 --> 00:35:20.650
Minsan akong nagsanay sa ilalim ng Tang Clan.

00:35:21.110 --> 00:35:22.740
Hindi ako mag-iiwan ng anumang bakas.

00:35:22.960 --> 00:35:23.820
Makakatiyak ka.

00:35:25.440 --> 00:35:26.380
Ang lason na ito

00:35:27.360 --> 00:35:28.530
ay ninakaw mula kay Prinsesa Ying

00:35:28.550 --> 00:35:30.420
ng isang undercover agent sa palasyo, hindi ba?

00:35:30.630 --> 00:35:31.260
Oo.

00:35:31.960 --> 00:35:32.900
narinig ko

00:35:33.320 --> 00:35:34.860
Bumisita na ang kanyang kamahalan sa malamig na palasyo

00:35:35.360 --> 00:35:37.170
at parang nalinis na si Prinsesa Ying.

00:35:37.960 --> 00:35:38.900
Hindi mahalaga.

00:35:39.440 --> 00:35:40.610
Nang walang matibay na patunay,

00:35:41.000 --> 00:35:43.050
kahit na may hinala ang Kanyang Kamahalan,

00:35:43.070 --> 00:35:43.860
kasong ito

00:35:44.230 --> 00:35:46.300
maiiwan lang na nakabitin.

00:35:50.360 --> 00:35:50.940
Magsalita.

00:35:53.760 --> 00:35:54.530
aking panginoon,

00:35:55.190 --> 00:35:56.380
itong Frostflower poison

00:35:56.480 --> 00:35:57.490
ay hindi kapani-paniwalang mabisyo.

00:35:57.840 --> 00:35:59.610
Kung ginamit nang walang ingat, maaari itong magdulot ng buhay.

00:36:00.150 --> 00:36:02.820
Talaga bang hindi ka nag-aalala tungkol sa Young Lady?

00:36:09.920 --> 00:36:11.820
Kung mayroon kang isang anak na babae

00:36:14.070 --> 00:36:16.170
na lumaking patas at matalino,

00:36:16.190 --> 00:36:17.820
pinapahalagahan tulad ng isang perlas sa iyong palad,

00:36:21.480 --> 00:36:22.860
pwede ba wag kang mag alala,

00:36:24.150 --> 00:36:25.340
hindi nakakaramdam ng sakit?

00:36:26.280 --> 00:36:29.010
Matagal ko nang inihanda ang antidote.

00:36:32.070 --> 00:36:33.340
Sa huling round,

00:36:34.150 --> 00:36:35.650
natalo ako.

00:36:37.400 --> 00:36:38.850
Kaya nagpasya ako

00:36:40.000 --> 00:36:41.490
para maglagay ng isa pang taya.

00:36:42.280 --> 00:36:44.340
I bet na may ibang nararamdaman para kay Cangcang

00:36:46.230 --> 00:36:47.820
tumakbo ng mas malalim

00:36:49.230 --> 00:36:50.010
kaysa sa akin.

00:36:51.320 --> 00:36:52.210
Nagsusugal siya.

00:36:52.800 --> 00:36:54.050
Salita tungkol sa Frost Reed

00:36:54.230 --> 00:36:55.420
dapat nag-leak out.

00:36:56.280 --> 00:36:57.260
Siya ay tumataya

00:36:57.510 --> 00:37:00.050
na hindi lang ako tatayo at panoorin ang pagkamatay ni Cangcang,

00:37:01.030 --> 00:37:02.570
na talagang gagamitin ko ang Frost Reed

00:37:02.840 --> 00:37:04.090
upang iligtas ang kanyang buhay.

00:37:05.150 --> 00:37:05.980
At sa sandaling gawin ko,

00:37:06.590 --> 00:37:08.050
Hindi na ako mabubuhay ng mas matagal.

00:37:08.710 --> 00:37:10.340
Kaya niyang i-pin ang lahat kay Xiao Ying,

00:37:10.840 --> 00:37:13.210
at pumukaw pa ng alitan sa pagitan ko at ng Empress Dowager.

00:37:13.840 --> 00:37:14.860
At pagkatapos noon,

00:37:15.590 --> 00:37:17.740
kung ang Empress ay naglihi sa aking tagapagmana,

00:37:18.150 --> 00:37:19.210
nitong round

00:37:19.670 --> 00:37:21.420
talagang magiging tatlong ibon na may isang bato.

00:37:22.880 --> 00:37:23.690
Tungkol dito,

00:37:25.030 --> 00:37:26.820
